This Map Is currently being hosted on my CS:S custom map server.
Server IP:
206.123.95.123:27015

This is probably the only map I actually put time into and even then its not good because I'm still a beginner with hammer.

The doors dont show up in the screenshots but yes there are really doors in the doorways, all of them that I know of are functional.

A.I. don't really like the doors too much, they like to camp and get stuck in them and open and close them constantly so human players are probably a better idea, although you can still play with A.I. but they tend to follow the same strategy every round.

Hostages also have an issue with doors so you may have a hard time rescuing them but there are also 2 bomb zones on this map for the terrorist team to use but because of the maps layout people will probably end up killing each other before any team completes its objective.

Development of this map has not been stoped i still try to fix errors that I find and add in additional features.

The map is not very big its about 1mb when its not compressed
